:: Aftermath1 {"position":"4100,600","size":"100,100"}
Confused, she turns to where the man was just standing.
As she turns, I get a glimpse of her face. The blood splatter got her good. It's dripping down her face and on to the pavement.

Her shirt and pants, once pink and blue respectively, are now the same deep shade of red.

She looks down at what is now a lifeless corpse.
I read the words off her lips.

"Daddy?"

My phone buzzes.

[[Check phone->MissionComplete]]


:: Aftermath2 {"position":"4100,800","size":"100,100"}
Without a second's hesitation, the man grabs his daughter and breaks for the SUV he arrived in. He nearly rips the door off its hinges, throws his daughter inside, and leaps in after her.

The SUV takes off and I quickly lose visual.

My phone buzzes.

[[Check phone->MissionFailed]]


:: CallBoss {"position":"2400,800","size":"100,100"}
I pull back from my rifle for the first time in fifteen minutes, pull out my phone, and dial Boss.

It rings.
It rings again.
It rings a third time, and then...

Silence.

[[Boss?->PhoneCall1]]


:: FinalDecision {"position":"3400,800","size":"100,100"}
I focus back up into the scope of my rifle. It's now or never.

[[Take the shot, hit him.->Kill]]
[[Take the shot, miss him.->Spare]]


:: Focus {"position":"1200,800","size":"100,100"}
I try to slow my breathing and focus, though the sizzling air is working tirelessly against me. Checking my pulse, it's a tad higher than the ideal sixty beats per minute, instead hovering at around seventy-five. Damn. Can't screw this one up, Rohan.

[[Continue...->TimeCheck]] 


:: Height {"position":"1200,1000","size":"100,100"}
I look down toward the asphalt grid below. It's a long way down. Thirty stories at least. Not great. I'd like to avoid a repeat of Budapest if possible. Shit got out of hand real quick back then.

[[Continue...->TimeCheck]] 


:: Indecisive {"position":"2200,600","size":"100,100"}
I start applying pressure to the trigger, but someting stops me from pulling it all the way.

This doesn't feel right.

[[Shake it off and squeeze.->Kill]]
[[I should call Boss.->CallBoss]]


:: Kill {"position":"3900,600","size":"100,100"}
BANG.

I squeeze the trigger, and a single shot rings out.
Everyone in a two hundred foot radius flinches.
His body ragdolls as the impact of the shot throws him five or six feet forward.

I see the child.

[[Continue...->Aftermath1]]


:: Meandering {"position":"1600,800","size":"100,100"}
Minutes pass, and while waiting I notice all the parkgoers happily going about their day. Some are with their partners, some are pushing strollers, and some are sitting sipping iced tea. Pity. None of them have any idea that the entire park is about to be an active crime scene. Oh well, used to be me. Before all this.

And as if on cue, the red SUV pulls up to the park. The left rear passenger door opens, and out steps our man. I lock my aim to his forehead as he walks around the vehicle. Easy shot. But then, he opens the right rear passenger door, and...

What the hell...?

[[Continue...->Twist]] 


