:: PhoneCall3 {"position":"3000,800","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:red)["And? I pay you to kill people, not run a daycare. That's how this works, remember? I give you names of people, those people die, and the Department gives you money."]

(text-colour:red)["Take the shot, Rohan. This is the job."]

[[Fine, but I want a bonus for this.->PhoneCall4A]]
[[I'm in the business of assassinating people, not traumatizing little girls. This wasn't part of the plan.->PhoneCall4B]]



:: PhoneCall4A {"position":"3200,700","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:red)["Your bonus is that you remain employed with us."]

The line goes dead.

[[Fuck.->FinalDecision]]


:: PhoneCall4B {"position":"3200,900","size":"100,100"}
(text-colour:red)["You of all people should know things don't always go according to plan. After Budapest, I thought you'd have learned how to adapt when that happens."]

(text-colour:red)["This is our one shot. You either get him today or he's in the wind."]

The line goes dead.

[[Fuck.->FinalDecision]]


