I lie prone on the rooftop, my back to the sky, and the scorching summer sun reveals itself from behind the clouds once again. A few beads of sweat streak down the back of my neck as I fiddle with the scope of my rifle.

[[Wipe the sweat away->Wipe]]
[[Try to focus->Focus]] 
[[Check height->Height]] 


:: Spare {"position":"3900,800","size":"100,100"}
BANG.

I squeeze the trigger, and a single shot rings out.
Everyone in a two hundred foot radius flinches.

The concrete path in front of the man explodes as the bullet strikes it.

[[Continue...->Aftermath2]]


:: TakeAim {"position":"2000,600","size":"100,100"}
Fuck it, orders are orders. This is the mission. This is the job. Guy wants his daughter to see his head pop like a tomato thrown against a wall? Not my problem.

I take deadly aim and a deep breath.

[[Pull the trigger->Kill]]
[[No, wait->Indecisive]]


:: TimeCheck {"position":"1400,800","size":"100,100"}
I glance briefly at my watch before I park my gaze back within my scope. It should be any moment now. One more name off the list.

[[Continue->Meandering]] 


:: Twist {"position":"1800,800","size":"100,100"}
...A child steps out of the vehicle.

The child, easily no older than eight, runs to the man who picks her up and, with a smile, squeezes her tight before putting her back down. He takes her hand and they start walking.

Son of a bitch brought his daughter to his own assassination.

[[Focus up and aim->TakeAim]]
[[Call this in to Boss->CallBoss]]


:: Wipe {"position":"1200,600","size":"100,100"}
I wipe the sweat from my neck and forehead. Much better, but there's more where that came from and it won't take very long. Yuck. I hate this part of the job.

[[Continue...->TimeCheck]] 
